snippet.title: DYNASTY WARRIORS DS: FIGHTER'S BATTLE TRAILER
snippet.description:
Only the toughest fighters will survive. Team up with some of your favourite Dynasty Warriors and build your deck of warriros cards to find the most powerful skills. The first Dynasty Warriors game to storm onto the DS is like no other game in the series.

Official Site: http://koei.com/dwds
Platform(s): Nintendo DS

Best Regards,
KOEI Ltd. - http://koei.co.uk
